[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":793},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":770,"related:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":779},"\u002Fen\u002Fcss\u002F2020\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcss-design-patterns-oocss\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":755,"date":756,"description":18,"extension":757,"lang":758,"meta":759,"navigation":330,"path":760,"readingMinutes":761,"seo":762,"standalone":763,"stem":764,"tags":765,"tldr":767,"updated":767,"url":768,"__hash__":769},"content\u002FCSS\u002F淺談-CSS-設計模式系列-OOCSS-篇.md","淺談 CSS 設計模式系列-OOCSS 篇","168089779",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":748},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,36,39,42,84,87,91,94,262,286,392,398,421,424,428,431,434,497,500,574,592,606,727,730,733,744],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"OOCSS 是 CSS 設計模式的另一種，其中最主要代表的框架就是 Bootstrap。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"oocss","OOCSS",[16,24,25],{},"OOCSS 全名是 「Object Oriented CSS」，中文的意思大概是「物件導向 CSS」，另一種中文翻譯是「面向對象 CSS」，其主要設計理念為兩者",[27,28,29,33],"ul",{},[30,31,32],"li",{},"Separation of content from container - 內容與容器的分離",[30,34,35],{},"Separation of structure from skin - 結構與樣式的分離",[16,37,38],{},"透過這兩個設計裡面可以大大增加 CSS 的擴充性以及 CSS 彈性，因此只要你有使用過 Bootstrap，那麼你就已經在無形中學習了 OOCSS 因為 Bootstrap 就是採用 OOCSS 設計，簡單來講就是每一個 class 他都可以獨立的運作。",[16,40,41],{},"舉例來講你不需要懂 CSS 你只需要看手冊，你就可以使用 Bootstrap 來套用樣式",[43,44,49],"pre",{"className":45,"code":46,"language":47,"meta":48,"style":48},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\u003Ch1 class=\"text-left text-danger d-flex\">這是一個 h1\u003C\u002Fh1>\n","html","",[50,51,52],"code",{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,54,57,61,65,69,72,76,79,81],"span",{"class":55,"line":56},"line",1,[53,58,60],{"class":59},"sMAXC","\u003C",[53,62,64],{"class":63},"sKpQp","h1",[53,66,68],{"class":67},"sCcAr"," class",[53,70,71],{"class":59},"=",[53,73,75],{"class":74},"sTRMh","\"text-left text-danger d-flex\"",[53,77,78],{"class":59},">這是一個 h1\u003C\u002F",[53,80,64],{"class":63},[53,82,83],{"class":59},">\n",[16,85,86],{},"因此 OOCSS 的設計裡面每一個 class 都是一個可以直接使用的 CSS 獨立個體，在這邊其實也與 SMACSS 的 Module 非常雷同。",[12,88,90],{"id":89},"separation-of-content-from-container-內容與容器的分離","Separation of content from container (內容與容器的分離)",[16,92,93],{},"在「內容與容器的分離」中有一個重點觀念，不要被排版版型限制，所謂被排版版型限制的意思如下方程式碼",[43,95,99],{"className":96,"code":97,"language":98,"meta":48,"style":48},"language-scss shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast",".header {\n  color: yellow;\n  width: 50px;\n  height: 50px;\n}\n.content {\n  color: red;\n  width: 50x;\n  height: 50px;\n}\n.footer {\n  color: blue;\n  width: 50px;\n  height: 50px;\n}\n","scss",[50,100,101,109,124,141,155,161,169,181,193,206,211,219,231,244,257],{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,102,103,106],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,104,105],{"class":67},".header",[53,107,108],{"class":59}," {\n",[53,110,112,115,118,121],{"class":55,"line":111},2,[53,113,114],{"class":67},"  color",[53,116,117],{"class":59},": ",[53,119,120],{"class":67},"yellow",[53,122,123],{"class":59},";\n",[53,125,127,130,132,135,139],{"class":55,"line":126},3,[53,128,129],{"class":67},"  width",[53,131,117],{"class":59},[53,133,134],{"class":67},"50",[53,136,138],{"class":137},"sWyjQ","px",[53,140,123],{"class":59},[53,142,144,147,149,151,153],{"class":55,"line":143},4,[53,145,146],{"class":67},"  height",[53,148,117],{"class":59},[53,150,134],{"class":67},[53,152,138],{"class":137},[53,154,123],{"class":59},[53,156,158],{"class":55,"line":157},5,[53,159,160],{"class":59},"}\n",[53,162,164,167],{"class":55,"line":163},6,[53,165,166],{"class":67},".content",[53,168,108],{"class":59},[53,170,172,174,176,179],{"class":55,"line":171},7,[53,173,114],{"class":67},[53,175,117],{"class":59},[53,177,178],{"class":67},"red",[53,180,123],{"class":59},[53,182,184,186,188,190],{"class":55,"line":183},8,[53,185,129],{"class":67},